<h1>Archive weather data from old weather station</h1>
<p>
  We previously had Davis weatherstation mounted on Lab II and then Seminar I.  This station ran from Tue May 04 22:00:00 -0700 1999 till Thu Nov 27 07:30:00 -0800 2008.
  The quality of the data is not great and you should look for anomolies in the data.  Below are the two records representing the oldest and newest data in the database.
  You can use the form at the bottom to query data from the database by setting a date range.  The data will download as a csv file with columns matching the data below.
</p>



